title: Jerry Garcia Band - 1982-06-24 - Capitol Theater in Passaic, NJ

Notes: 
This was the last JGB show with Bill Kreutzmann, Jimmy Warren, Essra Mowhawk, and Liz Stires. 


Some of the songs start abruptly due to tape pauses. The very end of Run for the Roses is clipped. Soundforge was used to make fades, adjust levels, and for some small edits. 

With big thanks to Jon P for transferring his DAT to CDR. EAC thru FLAC by Andrew F.                         
 ****ENJOY****
